{"tid":2275131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"神之子特朗普 已步入啟示錄預言","createTime":"2020-11-07T02:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T02:53:37.000Z","uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"975581c2f94d71e9262637852b4bfb081cc775a5","tid":2275131,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T02:49:56.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">大淫婦講緊邊個？ 大家應該明<br />\n解決完大淫婦，就會消滅隻紅龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n巴比倫大淫婦，是《新約聖經&middot;啟示錄》中提到的寓言式的邪惡人物， 她與敵基督與七頭十角的獸有關。「大淫婦」一詞，見於《啟示錄》第17章第1節、第5章、第18章以及第19章第2節。《啟示錄》第17章第1節載：「天使對約翰說：『你到這裏來，我將坐在眾水上的大淫婦所要受的刑罰指給你看。』」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">《啟示錄》第17章描述這個大淫婦說：<br />\n<br />\n「你到這裡來，我將坐在眾水上的大淫婦所要受的刑罰指給你看。地上的君王與她行淫，住在地上的人喝醉了她淫亂的酒。」（啟示錄17章1-2節聖經和合本）</span>"},{"pid":"3b96f9c97be703737fea3165ea3a0f92ff8e5758","tid":2275131,"uid":297230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T02:51:44.000Z","msg":"大淫婦=deep state<br />\n紅龍=chi na<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef122e9b4b1e3d774a593830afef68a146672fac","tid":2275131,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3b96f9c97be703737fea3165ea3a0f92ff8e5758","tid":2275131,"uid":297230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T02:51:44.000Z","msg":"大淫婦=deep state<br />\n紅龍=chi na<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T02:53:37.000Z","msg":"紅龍利用完班左膠，就會食佢既肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被處決<br />\n<br />\n天使對約翰談及大淫婦，説：「天使又對我說，你所看見那淫婦坐的眾水，就是多民、多人、多國、多方。你所看見的那十角與獸必恨這淫婦，使她冷落赤身，又要吃她的肉，用火將她燒盡。」（啟示錄17：15，16）"}]}